On the 13th of this month, a queue controversy occurred in Shanghai, China, a girl exposed her sexual body, but was accused of jumping into the line of netizens.
It is believed that this girl took part in an event, but she had to queue up at the center. Then there was a verbal conflict between the girl and everyone, and the girl even shouted: “I’m so good and I don’t want to be in a row!” Many people were surprised. But then the argument seemed to get stronger, and the girl became emotional and kept shouting at high decibels: “Excuse me, excuse me!”
Later, staff and security came to calm her down, and someone apologized to her at the scene, but the girl still seemed unable to calm down, and continued to make jokes and even saying, “I’m more beautiful than her.” It is reported that the police eventually took her away, but the video was immediately circulated by netizens and sparked heated discussions. a shrew.”, “She’s so cute!”, “Just because of her big breasts, I forgive her.”, “I really can’t do this.”
